<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 14:07:14 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列极右翼国家安全部长庆祝自 10 月 7 日以来发放了 10 万张持枪许可证</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/far-right-israeli-minister-celebrates-handing-out-100k-gun-permits-since-oct-7/0000018e-5682-dc6f-adff-df87a3ae0000</link><description>伊塔马尔·本·格维尔 (Itamar Ben Gvir) 表示，“在平民可以保护自己的地方，[10 月 7 日]灾难的严重程度没有那么严重。”他对武装以色列平民的宽松政策引起了广泛谴责</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 12:11:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/far-right-israeli-minister-celebrates-handing-out-100k-gun-permits-since-oct-7/0000018e-5682-dc6f-adff-df87a3ae0000</guid></item><item><title>如果以色列专注于军事行动，哈马斯将继续实现其目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-19/ty-article-opinion/.premium/hamas-will-continue-to-achieve-its-goals-if-israel-only-focuses-on-military-action/0000018e-566e-dc6f-adff-df6f4d730000</link><description>加沙战争实际上是社会战争，除非我们承认我们无法取得并维持成功</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 12:11:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-19/ty-article-opinion/.premium/hamas-will-continue-to-achieve-its-goals-if-israel-only-focuses-on-military-action/0000018e-566e-dc6f-adff-df6f4d730000</guid></item><item><title>拜登所做的一切都无法罢免内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/nothing-biden-does-can-remove-netanyahu/0000018e-55e9-d5d7-abae-55ff2b800000</link><description>以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡无力承担 10 月 7 日事件的责任，也无意辞职。除非他在议会中的对手们不齐心协力，否则任何外部压力都不会让他下台</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 12:07:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/nothing-biden-does-can-remove-netanyahu/0000018e-55e9-d5d7-abae-55ff2b800000</guid></item><item><title>救护车延误和交通堵塞：自加沙战争开始以来，以色列军队封锁了进入西岸村庄的通道</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/delayed-ambulances-and-long-trips-israeli-army-blocks-entry-to-west-bank-villages/0000018e-561a-d0e6-afbe-fe7e57a10000</link><description>一名志愿医务人员表示，“即使在紧急情况下，我们也无法通过检查站”，因为约旦河西岸的巴勒斯坦居民报告说，自 10 月 7 日以来，他们必须使用危险的土路并通知定居点才能出行。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 11:21:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/delayed-ambulances-and-long-trips-israeli-army-blocks-entry-to-west-bank-villages/0000018e-561a-d0e6-afbe-fe7e57a10000</guid></item><item><title>由于联盟关系紧张，赋予政府权力任命城市拉比的有争议法案被搁置</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/contentious-bill-giving-government-power-over-rabbi-posts-shelved-amid-coalition-tension/0000018e-555b-dfaa-af8e-d7dbccca0000</link><description>战时内阁部长本尼·甘茨表示，“我们必须围绕战争目标团结起来，不要参与会造成不和的有争议的立法”，各政治派别的立法者都对该法案的推迟表示欢迎</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 08:38:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/contentious-bill-giving-government-power-over-rabbi-posts-shelved-amid-coalition-tension/0000018e-555b-dfaa-af8e-d7dbccca0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列重返希法证明加沙北部哈马斯远未投降</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-return-to-shifa-proves-that-hamas-is-far-from-surrendering-in-northern-gaza/0000018e-5348-d37a-a1ae-5b68f4070000</link><description>该恐怖组织在加沙地带北部的势力已被瓦解。与此同时，卡塔尔正在进行的谈判很好地服务于内塔尼亚胡的生存目标，并危及那些仍然活着的人质</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 04:00:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-return-to-shifa-proves-that-hamas-is-far-from-surrendering-in-northern-gaza/0000018e-5348-d37a-a1ae-5b68f4070000</guid></item><item><title>以色列影响力行动针对哈马斯-近东救济工程处的美国议员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-03-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-influence-op-targets-u-s-lawmakers-on-hamas-unrwa/0000018e-5098-d282-a19f-7dd95cc70000</link><description>数百个虚假账户放大了三个神秘的“新闻网站”，以促进以色列的利益。他们的目标：美国民主党议员</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 04:00:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-03-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-influence-op-targets-u-s-lawmakers-on-hamas-unrwa/0000018e-5098-d282-a19f-7dd95cc70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布了在希法医院附近的加沙战斗中丧生的以色列士兵的姓名</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article-live/white-house-netanyahu-to-dispatch-team-to-discuss-rafah-invasion-in-coming-days/0000018e-5498-de3a-afdf-55f8365b0000</link><description>51 岁的以色列士兵塞巴斯蒂安·海昂 (Sebastian Haion) 在 Al-Shifa 医院的战斗中身亡 ■ 以色列国防军：180 人在 Al-Shifa 医院行动中被捕，50 人死亡，其中包括哈马斯高级武装分子 ■ 摩萨德酋长巴尼亚已离开多哈，以色列代表团仍在进行谈判 ■ 报道加沙称以色列暗杀了负责确保加沙北部援助的哈马斯官员 ■ 卡塔尔：对加沙停火谈判持谨慎乐观态度，但尚未接近达成协议</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 02:50:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article-live/white-house-netanyahu-to-dispatch-team-to-discuss-rafah-invasion-in-coming-days/0000018e-5498-de3a-afdf-55f8365b0000</guid></item><item><title>家人称，被监禁的巴勒斯坦领导人马尔万·巴尔古提被警卫“用棍棒殴打”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/jailed-palestinian-leader-marwan-barghouti-beaten-with-clubs-by-guards-family-claims/0000018e-5398-d37a-a1ae-5bf8d11b0000</link><description>以色列否认以不人道的条件关押法塔赫高级成员，他因谋杀罪在以色列服五次无期徒刑</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 22:28:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/jailed-palestinian-leader-marwan-barghouti-beaten-with-clubs-by-guards-family-claims/0000018e-5398-d37a-a1ae-5bf8d11b0000</guid></item><item><title>白宫证实哈马斯高级军事指挥官马尔万·伊萨上周在以色列对加沙的袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/white-house-hamas-deputy-military-chief-marwan-issa-was-killed-in-israeli-gaza-strike/0000018e-535e-d37a-a1ae-5b7ed5ca0000</link><description>尚未收到以色列关于伊萨死亡的官方确认。他是穆罕默德·代伊夫的得力助手，并担任哈马斯武装部队副总司令</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 21:57:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/white-house-hamas-deputy-military-chief-marwan-issa-was-killed-in-israeli-gaza-strike/0000018e-535e-d37a-a1ae-5b7ed5ca0000</guid></item><item><title>特朗普：任何投票给民主党的犹太人都讨厌他们的宗教，应该为自己感到羞耻</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/trump-jews-who-vote-for-democrats-hate-everything-about-israel-should-be-ashamed/0000018e-5371-dca4-ad8e-f7ff5c090000</link><description>白宫猛烈抨击前总统“卑鄙且精神错乱的反犹太主义言论”</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 21:31:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/trump-jews-who-vote-for-democrats-hate-everything-about-israel-should-be-ashamed/0000018e-5371-dca4-ad8e-f7ff5c090000</guid></item><item><title>拜登与内塔尼亚胡通话后，美国拒绝拉法“稻草人”论点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/u-s-rejects-rafah-straw-man-argument-after-biden-netanyahu-call/0000018e-5300-dca4-ad8e-f7fee8f60000</link><description>拜登总统结束一个多月以来与内塔尼亚胡的首次通话后不久，美国国家安全顾问杰克·沙利文表示，以色列总理反对在拉法采取重大军事行动类似于反对彻底击败哈马斯的立场是“无稽之谈”</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 19:55:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/u-s-rejects-rafah-straw-man-argument-after-biden-netanyahu-call/0000018e-5300-dca4-ad8e-f7fee8f60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙城 Al-Shifa 医院袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-killed-in-combat-during-al-shifa-hospital-raid-in-gaza-city/0000018e-52df-d282-a19f-7fdfcfc50000</link><description>根据陆军记录，20 岁的参谋军士。来自耶路撒冷的马坦·维诺格拉多夫是自 10 月地面行动开始以来第 250 名阵亡士兵</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 19:49:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-killed-in-combat-during-al-shifa-hospital-raid-in-gaza-city/0000018e-52df-d282-a19f-7fdfcfc50000</guid></item><item><title>欧盟“一致”同意对暴力的以色列约旦河西岸定居者实施制裁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/eu-unanimously-agrees-to-impose-sanctions-against-violent-israeli-west-bank-settlers/0000018e-52c2-dc23-a3bf-daf760d20000</link><description>这一举措是继美国和英国之后，得到欧盟所有27个成员国同意的。它涉及对约旦河西岸“暴力”以色列定居者的旅行禁令和资产冻结，并禁止欧盟公民与目标开展业务</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 18:59:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/eu-unanimously-agrees-to-impose-sanctions-against-violent-israeli-west-bank-settlers/0000018e-52c2-dc23-a3bf-daf760d20000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日的隐形受害者：即使死亡，以色列的寻求庇护者也得不到承认</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-invisible-victims-of-oct-7-even-in-death-asylum-seekers-in-israel-arent-recognized/0000018e-5277-db53-a39e-daf704f30000</link><description>吉吉、泰格和彪马逃离厄立特里亚和达尔富尔，获准在以色列生活，但没有合法身份或权利。 10月7日他们被哈马斯杀害后，国家拒绝将他们视为恐怖主义受害者</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 18:19:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-invisible-victims-of-oct-7-even-in-death-asylum-seekers-in-israel-arent-recognized/0000018e-5277-db53-a39e-daf704f30000</guid></item><item><title>您需要了解的第 164 天：以色列拒绝近东救济工程处主要人员进入加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/what-you-need-to-know-day-164-israel-denies-unrwa-chief-entry-to-gaza/0000018e-52aa-dca4-ad8e-f6fe40a10001</link><description>摩萨德负责人抵达卡塔尔，就释放人质/停火协议进行新一轮谈判 ■ 以色列国防军称，“具体证据”显示哈马斯正在使用希法医院，因此在袭击中逮捕了 80 多人 ■ 以色列拒绝近东救济工程处负责人入境前往加沙 ■ 内塔尼亚胡总理一个多月来首次与拜登通电话，但没有像往常一样发布谈话内容 ■ 战争结束 164 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 17:51:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/what-you-need-to-know-day-164-israel-denies-unrwa-chief-entry-to-gaza/0000018e-52aa-dca4-ad8e-f6fe40a10001</guid></item><item><title>以色列队抵达卡塔尔；以色列高级官员称，哈马斯领导人辛瓦尔将参与会谈</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-team-touches-down-in-qatar-for-next-round-of-gaza-talks-with-hamas/0000018e-524e-dfaa-af8e-d3cf36aa0000</link><description>一位以色列高级政治消息人士称，谈判将“直接与哈马斯领导人叶海亚·辛瓦尔”进行，而不是与调解人进行，预计将需要“至少两周”</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 17:41:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-team-touches-down-in-qatar-for-next-round-of-gaza-talks-with-hamas/0000018e-524e-dfaa-af8e-d3cf36aa0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登和比比打架，特朗普和共和党闻到了血腥味</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-18/ty-article/.highlight/biden-and-bibi-are-fighting-and-trump-and-the-gop-smell-blood/0000018e-51f5-dfaa-af8e-d3ffd7db0001</link><description>随着民主党和内塔尼亚胡之间的紧张关系呈指数级增长，与加沙的死亡人数同步，以色列总理希望急于利用这场危机打击拜登的特朗普和共和党能为他提供政治救生筏</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 17:31:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-18/ty-article/.highlight/biden-and-bibi-are-fighting-and-trump-and-the-gop-smell-blood/0000018e-51f5-dfaa-af8e-d3ffd7db0001</guid></item><item><title>两名以色列试管婴儿实验室负责人因涉嫌故意进口携带遗传病的卵子而被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/two-israeli-ivf-lab-heads-arrested-for-allegedly-knowingly-importing-eggs-with-disease/0000018e-51d7-dca4-ad8e-f5ff250c0000</link><description>调查是在一名患者死产、另一名患者生下一名患有血友病的婴儿后开始的。以色列卫生部现在命令体外受精部门寻找从同一诊所接受卵子的妇女，以便告知她们风险</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 17:26:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/two-israeli-ivf-lab-heads-arrested-for-allegedly-knowingly-importing-eggs-with-disease/0000018e-51d7-dca4-ad8e-f5ff250c0000</guid></item><item><title>联合国支持的报告称，加沙很快将面临饥荒；欧盟高级外交官指责以色列“挑起”饥饿</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/un-report-gaza-will-soon-face-famine-eu-top-diplomat-blames-israel-of-provoking-hunger/0000018e-5229-dfaa-af8e-d3eb3d060000</link><description>报告称，加沙约有一半人口目前面临“灾难性饥饿”。联合国敦促人道主义援助完全进入加沙，官员们称这是一场“人为”灾难。与此同时，以色列表示问题在于援助的分配</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 16:22:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/un-report-gaza-will-soon-face-famine-eu-top-diplomat-blames-israel-of-provoking-hunger/0000018e-5229-dfaa-af8e-d3eb3d060000</guid></item></channel></rss>